---
// Privacy policy (Phase E, Step 17). A GDPR-aware TEMPLATE for client/legal review. My own prose:
// no em dashes. Placeholders (email, retention period) are flagged and must be completed/reviewed
// by Northaxis and a qualified legal adviser before launch.
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/ui/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
import TriangleAlert from 'lucide-astro/TriangleAlert';

const crumbs = [{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Privacy policy' }];
const lastUpdated = '17 June 2026';

const description =
  'How Northaxis Integrated Services collects, uses, and protects personal data submitted through this website. Template for review.';
---

<Base title="Privacy policy | Northaxis Integrated Services" description={description}>
  <PageHero crumbs={crumbs} headline="Privacy policy" />

  <Section bg="white" width="narrow" space="lg">
    <div class="nx-review" role="note">
      <span class="nx-review__icon" aria-hidden="true"><TriangleAlert /></span>
      <p>
        <strong>Template for client and legal review.</strong> This draft policy must be reviewed
        and approved by Northaxis and a qualified legal adviser before the website goes live. Items
        marked <span class="nx-ph">[like this]</span> need to be completed or confirmed.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="nx-legal">
      <p class="nx-legal__updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        Northaxis Integrated Services Limited ("Northaxis", "we", "us", "our") is the data
        controller for personal data collected through this website. We are a CAC-registered company
        based in {SITE.location}. You can contact us about this policy at
        <span class="nx-ph">[{SITE.emailPlaceholder}, email to be confirmed]</span>.
      </p>

      <h2>What this policy covers</h2>
      <p>
        This policy explains what personal data we collect when you use this website, why we collect
        it, how we use and protect it, and the rights you have. It applies to this website only.
      </p>

      <h2>The data we collect</h2>
      <p>
        When you submit a contact or enquiry form, we collect the information you provide. This
        typically includes your name, your organisation, your email address, your phone number, and
        the details of your message or requirement.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you browse the website, we may collect limited technical data such as your device type,
        browser, approximate location, and the pages you visit. We only collect analytics data of
        this kind after you accept analytics cookies.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use your data</h2>
      <p>
        We use your data to respond to your enquiry, to provide the information or services you
        request, to keep records of our communications, and to improve the website. Where you have
        consented, we use analytics data to understand how the website is used so we can make it
        more useful.
      </p>

      <h2>Our legal basis</h2>
      <p>
        Where you submit an enquiry, we process your data on the basis of your request to us and our
        legitimate interest in responding to potential and existing clients. Where we use analytics
        cookies, we process data on the basis of your consent, which you can withdraw at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses a small number of essential cookies that are required for it to work.
        These do not track you. With your consent, we also use analytics cookies that help us
        understand how the website is used. No analytics cookies, and no third party tracking, are
        set until you accept them using the cookie banner. You can change your choice at any time by
        clearing this website's data in your browser.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics 4 to measure website usage. Analytics only loads after you accept
        analytics cookies. The data is used in aggregate to understand traffic and improve the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Maps</h2>
      <p>
        Our contact page can show a Google Maps embed so you can find our office. The map only loads
        after you accept cookies. If you prefer, you can open the location directly in Google Maps
        using the link provided, without loading the embed.
      </p>

      <h2>Third parties we work with</h2>
      <p>We use trusted third party services to operate this website:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our hosting provider, which serves the website.</li>
        <li>Our email delivery provider, which sends us the messages you submit through our forms.</li>
        <li>Google Analytics, which measures website usage after you consent.</li>
        <li>Google Maps, which displays our location on the contact page after you consent.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These providers process data on our behalf or under their own terms. We do not sell your
        personal data to anyone.
      </p>

      <h2>How long we keep your data</h2>
      <p>
        We keep enquiry data for as long as needed to respond to you and to maintain a record of our
        business communications, after which we delete or anonymise it.
        <span class="nx-ph">[Retention period to be confirmed by Northaxis.]</span>
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Subject to applicable law, you have the right to ask us for a copy of your data, to correct
        it, to delete it, to restrict or object to how we use it, and to receive it in a portable
        format. Where we rely on your consent, you can withdraw it at any time. To exercise any of
        these rights, contact us using the details below.
      </p>

      <h2>Keeping your data secure</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your data. The website
        is served over a secure HTTPS connection. No method of transmission or storage is completely
        secure, but we work to protect your information against unauthorised access, loss, or misuse.
      </p>

      <h2>International transfers</h2>
      <p>
        Some of our third party providers may process data outside Nigeria. Where they do, we rely
        on the safeguards those providers put in place to protect your data.
      </p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        This website is intended for business and government users and is not directed at children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. The date at the top shows when it was last
        updated.
      </p>

      <h2>How to contact us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this policy or wish to exercise your rights, contact us at
        <span class="nx-ph">[{SITE.emailPlaceholder}]</span> or by phone on {SITE.whatsappNumber}. If
        you believe we have not handled your data properly, you can also raise a complaint with the
        relevant data protection authority.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>

<style>
  .nx-review {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, #f6c000 14%, #fff);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, #f6c000 45%, var(--color-border));
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }
  .nx-review p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .nx-review__icon {
    color: #9a6b00;
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }
  .nx-review__icon :global(svg) {
    width: 1.3rem;
    height: 1.3rem;
  }

  .nx-legal__updated {
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-grey);
  }
  .nx-legal h2 {
    margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .nx-legal p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-grey);
  }
  .nx-legal ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-grey);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .nx-legal li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .nx-ph {
    color: var(--color-grey);
    font-style: italic;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-border) 30%, transparent);
    padding: 0 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
